Class StarterCard

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.card.Card
it.polimi.ingsw.model.card.PlayableCard
it.polimi.ingsw.model.card.StarterCard
public class StarterCard extends PlayableCard
A starter card is the first card placed on each player's board. At the start of the match, each player randomly draws one starter card from the deck.
